reviewText:
This is the second copy I ordered. Neither plays the second side. Grandsons watched How to Eat Fried Worms but when I flip it over,
nothing works. I bought this twice and only 1 out of the 3 movies can be viewed.https://www.amazon.com/dp/B002HFWB0S/ref=cm_cr_ryp_prd_ttl_sol_0
Great value for some fun movies! Thank You!
Great combo of family friendly movies.
This was a good purchase. Inexpensive, wholesome movies for a sleep over party.
